# ThePixStock - Go-to-Market Strategy & Growth Plan

## 🚀 **Phase 1: Pre-Launch Preparation (Week 1-4)**

### **Market Research & Validation**
```
Target Market Analysis:
📊 Wedding Photography Market in Thailand
├── Market Size: ~15,000 weddings/month in Thailand
├── Average Wedding Photos: 800-1,500 per event
├── Current Pain Points: Manual photo delivery, slow customer search
├── Price Point Validation: 60฿/200฿/500฿ packages
└── Photographer Survey: 50+ photographers interviewed

Competition Analysis:
🏢 Direct Competitors
├── SmugMug: $40-60/month subscription
├── Pixieset: $15-30/month per event
├── ShootProof: $10-25/month
└── Local Solutions: Manual USB/CD delivery

Competitive Advantages:
✨ Our Unique Value Props
├── AI Face Recognition (ไม่มีคู่แข่งในไทย)
├── Thai Language Support
├── PromptPay Integration  
├── Baht Currency Native
└── Local Payment Methods
```

### **Beta Testing Program**
```python
# Beta Tester Recruitment Strategy
beta_program = {
